{"tid":1567474,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【果燃台3pm LIVE】藍絲號召去淘大唱國歌 傳逾百黑社會將到場製「7.21元朗恐襲2.0」","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:41:59.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b7376b0e06264d80b5f2266caf00177887541ced","tid":1567474,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n淘大商場街坊日前（11日）聚集齊唱《願榮光歸香港》，有中年男子帶同3名年幼子女到場，突然唱國歌和近攝他人容貌，挑釁和指罵街坊，不但令其子女受驚，更與人爭執打鬥受傷。該涉事男子被網民發現為東華三院王余家潔紀念小學李姓教師。一批藍絲號召今午3時到淘大商場聚集合唱國歌，但多次採訪反送中運動的英籍記者Richard Scotford在facebook貼出一張對話截圖，對方引述一個「可信消息」指有逾百名香港及澳門黑社會成員今午3時將到淘大商場集合唱國歌，但實際目的是製造「7.21元朗恐襲2.0」，意指將會發生再度無差別襲擊市民的事件，叮囑Richard要小心。《蘋果》屆時將直播淘大情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fabdb4d8d4f59466a52c272b889ab35dc527bfa","tid":1567474,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6v9Jdp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6v9Jdp.jpg&h=6cbe719f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJFtYML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJFtYML.jpg&h=a79b44b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89f4832a6a21c27b13fec8b406569d4d6538543f","tid":1567474,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc0692767615ed2522e70c712b7a86beab080b9","tid":1567474,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d9446bb7f7f686750808278bf59a5abe1a70e